 Your Majesty, to grow so weary and despairing.

256
00:19:25,690 --> 00:19:30,670
 For you too, a day when you might have to retreat.

257
00:19:30,670 --> 00:19:36,000
 All I can do is to wish, with all the loyalty in my heart,

258
00:19:38,070 --> 00:19:43,930
